Package: hamapi
Type: Package
Title: Download Artwork Information from Harvard Art Museum API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Melodie", "He", email = "yuxiu.he@yahoo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is based on the Harvard Art Museum API.
    It allows the user to receive a list of artwork information 
    (title, object id, period, century, culture, division,
    corresponding website url, image url, classification, department) by specifying 
    the classification of artworks the user interested in. 
    Allows user to download image of artworks from get_artwork_info function(coming)
    Allows user to obtain information about gallery in each floor of the museum.
    Allows user to obtain the information of which gallery has most artwork collections.
